high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk in the study room.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn around and go near the mug in the kitchen wardrobe.
Put the knife into the mug on the wardrobe.
Take the mug along with the knife from the wardrobe.
Turn around and go near the countertop.
Put the mug with knife on the countertop near the oven.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Mug with Knife on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Leave the room. Turn left. When you reach the desk, turn left.
Take the knife.
Return to the room. Turn right when you reach the refrigerator. Approach the mug cabinet.
Open the left door of the upper cabinet. Place the knife in the mug.
Take the mug and the knife. Close the door.
Turn right, move forward. Turn around.
Place the mug and knife on the left side of the countertop, next to the wall.
anns.task_desc: Find a Knife and a Mug. Place them near the CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn back and come out of the kitchen and on the left side, there is a study room, enter into it. Then, reach the desk.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn back and come out of the room and enter into the kitchen again. Walk straight and then turn right to reach the mug cupboard.
Open the cupboard and place the knife in the mug.
Take out the mug along with the knife and then close the cupboard.
Reach the microwave oven which is next to the countertop.
Place the mug on the countertop next to the microwave oven.
anns.task_desc: Place the Mug with Knife next to the CounterTop
